&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; On Fri, Nov 7, 2025 at 2:44 PM Johann Hofmann &lt;&lt;a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="2f4540474e41410101016f48404048434a014c4042"&gt;[email&#160;protected]&lt;/a&gt;&gt;
