On Thu, Nov 27, 2025, 6:31 p.m. Jeremy Roman &lt;&lt;a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="573d35253879797917343f25383a3e223a79382530"&gt;[email&#160;protected]&lt;/a&gt;&gt; wrote:

&gt; I guess I'm not sure I'm asking anything be done now that this is done,
&gt; but I'm a bit surprised we unwound a longstanding technical decision so
&gt; suddenly.
