&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; interest.
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; I for one was interested in this format and the improvements it would 
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; bring, and it seems many others are disappointed too.  Can Google explain 
