&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; interest? Even this intent to prototype lists many of the purported 
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; benefits and the extent of the interest, which makes this reversal 
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; particularly hard to understand.
