&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; crbug requesting the feature. A lot of interest on encode.su 
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="http://encode.su"&gt;http://encode.su&lt;/a&gt;&gt;, r/jpegxl, &lt;&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://reddit.com/r/jpegxl/"&gt;https://reddit.com/r/jpegxl/&lt;/a&gt;&gt; discord 
