It’s been a while since v139 was released. We’ve noticed that some Windows machines are now using WARP, and SwiftShader appears to be disabled on certain Linux machines. We are currently developing some backup plans to address the SwiftShader disablement. May we ask a few follow-up questions we’ve encountered?&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre&gt;
