&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; &lt;a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="d7aeb8b6a1f9f9f997b4bfa5b8babea2baf9b8a5b0"&gt;[email&#160;protected]&lt;/a&gt;&gt; wrote:
