&gt; On Wed, Nov 19, 2025 at 4:20 PM Daniel Bratell &lt;&lt;a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="e684948792838ac8c8c8a6818b878f8ac885898b"&gt;[email&#160;protected]&lt;/a&gt;&gt;
