&gt; On Wed, Oct 15, 2025 at 11:25 AM Vladimir Levin &lt;&lt;a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="7d0b100d5353533d1e150f121014081053120f1a"&gt;[email&#160;protected]&lt;/a&gt;&gt;
