&lt;pre&gt;LGTM3

On Wed, Nov 5, 2025 at 5:33 PM Yoav Weiss (@Shopify) &lt;&lt;a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="61180e001716044f4f4f210209130e0c08140c4f0e1306"&gt;[email&#160;protected]&lt;/a&gt;&gt;
