&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; *WebKit*: No signal
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; *Web developers*: Strongly positive (
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/Locale/variants"&gt;https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/Locale/variants&lt;/a&gt;
